NAME
       Sledge::Template::ClearSilver - ClearSilver template system for Sledge

SYNOPSIS
         package MyApp::Pages;
         use strict;
         use base qw(Sledge::Pages::Apache);
         use Sledge::Template::ClearSilver

DESCRIPTION
       Sledge::Template::ClearSilver is ClearSilver template system for Sledge.

